      "text": "\ud83d\udcb0 CRYPTO: A DeFi (decentralized finance) protocol called Ostium just lost $18 million to an oracle exploit -- the latest in a wave of similar attacks.\n\nOracles are the price feeds smart contracts rely on to know an asset's real value.",
